1. Open a new shell
2. Get and save the ip address of Aiur
	docker-machine ip Aiur
3. ssh into Aiur
	docker-machine ssh Aiur
4. in the shell opened in Char copy the result of the command
	docker swarm join-token worker
5. The result of the above command should resemble "    docker swarm join --token SWMTKN-1-4z7d4v9s38pezunxqthcrpb6s217a4zdomc4msxmic3edq6w66-c79tllhjoaz5qbr30pvzj0s2q 192.168.99.100:2377"
	paste this in to the shell openend at Aiur
